ness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":799,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/05\/21\/valley-gold-still-wants-more\/","url_meta":{"origin":940,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Greed: If he had all the gold, he still wants more","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 21, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas bin Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"If the son of Adam had a valley full of gold, he would want to have two valleys. Nothing fills his mouth but the dust of the grave, yet Allah will relent to whoever repents\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26759,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/08\/15\/spend-sadaqah-not-bakhil\/","url_meta":{"origin":940,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Charity: Spend in charity, do not be miserly","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 15, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Asma\u2019 reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSpend in charity and do not count it, lest Allah count it against you. Do not hoard it, lest Allah withhold from you.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 2451, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1029 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\